President Cyril Ramaphosa meets German Chancellor Olaf Scholz at the Union Buildings in Pretoria. PRETORIA - President Cyril Ramaphosa is hosting German Chancellor Olaf Scholz. Olaf is on an official visit to the country, after visiting Senegal and Niger. It's likely that South Africa's non-alignment in the Ukraine-Russia conflict will come up. The leaders are also likely to discuss trade relations and tourism. President Cyril Ramaphosa meets German Chancellor Olaf Scholz at the Union Buildings in Pretoria.